---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - MindLooker">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p class="text-brand-muted mb-6">Last updated: January 2025</p>
      
      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">The Simple Version</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We respect your privacy. We collect only what we need to provide our services. 
          We don't sell your data. We protect what you share with us. That's it.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">What We Collect</h2>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Information You Provide</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Contact information when you book a session or apply for training</li>
          <li>Payment information (processed securely through third-party providers)</li>
          <li>Communications you send us</li>
          <li>Application information for practitioner training</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Information Collected Automatically</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Basic analytics (page views, referral sources)</li>
          <li>Technical information (browser type, device type)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>To provide the services you request</li>
          <li>To process bookings and payments</li>
          <li>To communicate about your sessions or training</li>
          <li>To improve our website and services</li>
          <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Session Confidentiality</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          What happens in your MindLooker session stays in your session. We maintain strict 
          confidentiality regarding all session content, with the following exceptions required by law:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Imminent risk of harm to yourself or others</li>
          <li>Suspected abuse of a child or vulnerable adult</li>
          <li>Court-ordered disclosure</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Note: MindLooker sessions are not medical or therapeutic treatment. See our 
          <a href="/legal/disclaimer" class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">disclaimer</a> for details.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Data Security</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We use industry-standard security measures to protect your information. This includes:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Encrypted data transmission (SSL/TLS)</li>
          <li>Secure third-party payment processing</li>
          <li>Limited access to personal information</li>
          <li>Regular security reviews</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We use selected third-party services to operate our business:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li><strong>Cal.com:</strong> For scheduling (see their privacy policy)</li>
          <li><strong>Payment processors:</strong> For secure payment handling</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> To understand website usage</li>
          <li><strong>Email services:</strong> For communications</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We choose partners who respect privacy and meet our security standards.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
          <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your information</li>
          <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
          <li>Request a copy of your data</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Cookies</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We use minimal cookies necessary for the website to function and to understand 
          how visitors use our site. You can control cookies through your browser settings.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We keep your information only as long as necessary to provide services and meet 
          legal requirements. Session notes (if any) are destroyed after the legally required 
          retention period.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Our services are not directed to children under 18. We do not knowingly collect 
          information from minors without parental consent.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We may update this policy from time to time. We'll notify you of significant 
          changes via email or website notice.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Questions about privacy? We're here to help:
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Email: privacy@mindlooker.com<br>
          Or use the contact form on our website
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-12 p-6 bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-sm text-brand-muted">
          <strong>Remember:</strong> This privacy policy covers our website and services. 
          It doesn't cover third-party sites we link to. Always review their policies too.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>